sentences: Having completed the consideration of the agenda item on Annex I parties further commitments late on Friday evening, parties adopted the meeting report (FCCC/KP/AWG/2010/L.3).
Thanking departing AWG-KP Vice-Chair Dovland and Claudio Forner from the Secretariat for their work under the AWG-KP, AWG-KP Chair Ashe closed the meeting at 10:01 pm.
